{"title":"The Made in Germany Nicolai Bikes Argon GX Gravel Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/02/the-made-in-germany-nicolai-bikes-argon-gx-gravel-bike/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-made-in-germany-nicolai-bikes-argon-gx-gravel-bike","date":1614008451000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-206089\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"The Made in Germany Nicolai Bikes Argon GX Gravel Bike\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/ARGON-GX_Bike_3000x2000_01-1780x1187-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>These days, gravel bike designs can be very redundant, something German manufacturers like Nicolai Bikes are looking to overcome. Their newest design, the Argon GX, is as much a gravel bike as it is a touring bike but look closely for some clever manufacturing detailing.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_3000x2000_3-scaled.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>Through 3D modeling and engineering, Nicolai is able to construct durable and lightweight 7020-T6 frame components. Each of these pieces are made on modern 5-axis CNC machines and allows for the construction of so-called “Hollow Mill” assemblages. The bottom bracket and chainstay yoke in the Argon CX use this technology to both shed weight and set their offerings apart from their competitors.</p><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon-GX_Brake_Flat-Mount-140-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/Argon_GX_Rack-and-Fender_1200x1200-1120x1120-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>Other details include the option for a Pinion gear box, fender/rack mounts, flat mount disc calipers, internal routing, and designed geometries to fit just about any body type. Head to <a href=\"https://en.nicolai-bicycles.com/bike/argon-gx/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Nicolai</a> to see more!</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"b2cecb17fca9dc75be337cff6223cffe6b6e962c86a2d5e2474490de2e3c6676","category":"Cycling"}